description: Demolition of all existing buildings and structures on site and the mixed-use redevelopment of the site to provide three buildings of ground-plus 6, ground-plus 5, and ground-plus 5 storeys respectively, including purpose-built student accommodation (Sui Generis), and commercial, business and service use (Use Class E), with basement level, access, parking, refuse and service areas, hard and soft landscaping, and associated works.
